<div class="help">

	<h4>Instructions to create a sspak file on your local development environment</h4>

	<p>
		Databases and assets snapshots are stored in deploynaut using the <a href="https://github.com/sminnee/sspak">sspak</a></a> format.
		You will need to install sspak onto your local machine if you wish to create these snapshots.</p>

	<pre>sspak save /path/to/my/local/site file.sspak</pre>

</div>
